| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7103 — Recovery Inhibition (play)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2aa2c3a6-1e99-5f10-befd-4cf3badaf4c1"
